Description: OpenBroadcaster - Cross-Platform Radio Automation Software
 OpenBroadcaster is a professional radio automation platform supporting
 multiple streaming platforms (Twitch, YouTube, etc.) with advanced
 audio processing and scheduling capabilities.
 .
 Features:
  - Multi-deck audio playback with professional mixing
  - Microphone input with ducking support
  - Top-of-Hour and Bottom-of-Hour automated injection
  - AutoDJ with smart rotation scheduling
  - DirectServer API for external control
  - Multi-platform support (Windows, Linux, macOS)
  - Comprehensive deck control and monitoring
  - Advanced audio routing and device management
